These '''tanks''' were used by the [[Death Watch/Legends|Death Watch]] during the [[Mandalorian Civil War (True Mandalorians)|Mandalorian Civil War]]. At least one was destroyed during the [[Battle of Concord Dawn]].
It had a pair of medium weapons on a turret, two smaller front-facing weapons and possibly a turreted missile launcher on the back. It was immune to small arms fire, but not from an explosive charge located on its belly.

